#ROOM
Vnum     42200
Name     &rThe Blackwing Overlook&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     You stand upon a high, secluded balcony deep within the upper 
reaches of Blackrock Spire. The air is thin and cold, and the 
entire mountain seems to vibrate with the hum of dark arcane 
machinery. To the north, a massive set of obsidian doors leads 
into the laboratory of Nefarian.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    36563
Desc      Return to the Hall of the Mountain in Searing Gorge.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    42201
Desc      The Hatchery Entrance.~
#ENDEXIT

#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     42201
Name     &rThe Blackwing Hatchery - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive circular chamber filled with hundreds of dark green 
and black eggs. The air is humid and smells of reptile musk. 
Blackwing technicians move frantically between control orbs, 
maintaining the stability of the brood. Razorgore the Untamed 
stands in the center, his mind controlled by the orcs.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    42202
Desc      The Hatchery Control Room.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    42200
Desc      The overlook.~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 42002 1 42201
Reset M 0 42009 10 42201
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     42202
Name     &rThe Hatchery Control Room&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A small stone room overlooking the hatchery floor. Several 
large crystal orbs glow with a sickly green light, used 
to dominate the minds of the dragonspawn. Blueprints 
of chromatic experiments are pinned to the walls.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    42203
Desc      The Burning Hall.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    42201
Desc      The hatchery.~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 42009 5 42202
Reset O 0 42116 10 42202
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     42203
Name     &rThe Burning Hall&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The temperature here is incredible. A wide thoroughfare 
leading through the center of the laboratory district. The 
noble red dragon Vaelastrasz writhes in the center of the 
hall, his sanity slipping away as the shadow-flame 
consumes his soul.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    42210
Desc      The Suppression Room.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    42202
Desc      The control room.~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 42003 1 42203
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     42210
Name     &rThe Suppression Room - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The air here feels heavy and slow. Dozens of small bronze 
pillars pulse with a green magical field, making every 
step feel like wading through mud. Laboratory assistants 
and whelps swarm the narrow paths between the traps.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    42211
Desc      Suppression Room Central.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    42203
Desc      The burning hall.~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 42015 10 42210
Reset M 0 42003 10 42210
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     42211
Name     &rThe Suppression Room - Central&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The heart of the magical gauntlet. The field of suppression 
is at its strongest here. To the north, a high stone ramp 
leads toward the Broodlord's seat.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    42212
Desc      The Broodlord's Balcony.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    42210
Desc      Suppression entry.~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 42015 10 42211
Reset M 0 42013 10 42211
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     42212
Name     &rThe Balcony of the Broodlord&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A high stone landing overlooking the entire suppression 
district. Broodlord Lashlayer stands here, his massive 
blade reflecting the orange glow of the mountain's core. 
He laughs as he watches the intruders struggle below.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    42220
Desc      The Dragon Laboratories.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
