  Reset G 1 42106 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     42220
Name     &rThe Dragon Laboratories - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The architecture here is grand and clinical. High-domed 
chambers are filled with massive brewing vats and 
anatomical models of dragons. Firemaw can be seen 
perched on a high bridge to the north.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    42221
Desc      The First Laboratory Bridge.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
