Desc      The broodlord's balcony.~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 42012 10 42220
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     42221
Name     &rThe First Laboratory Bridge&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A narrow stone span crossing a massive vertical shaft. 
Firemaw guards this bridge, his presence alone enough 
to heat the stone to a dull red glow.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    42222
Desc      The Second Laboratory Bridge.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
