#ROOM
Vnum     42230
Name     &rThe Kennel of Chromaggus&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive circular chamber filled with the smell of 
alchemy and ozone. Chromaggus stands in the center, 
his multiple heads shifting in and out of phase with 
the physical world. A large lever on the wall is the 
only way to release him from his magical shackles.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    42240
Desc      The Nefarian Overlook.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
