#ROOM
Vnum     42240
Name     &rThe Nefarian Overlook - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A series of high stone stairs leading to the open-air peak of 
the mountain. The air becomes noticeably fresher, but the 
sense of dread only increases. Lord Victor Nefarius sits 
upon a throne at the far end of the terrace.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    42241
Desc      The Throne of Nefarian.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
