Vnum     42241
Name     &rThe Throne of Lord Victor Nefarius&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The highest point of Blackrock Mountain. Lord Victor Nefarius 
sits upon a high throne, watching the combat below with 
amusement. This is the place of final judgment. If his 
guards fall, he will take to the air in his true 
form.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    42240
Desc      The overlook entry.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction up~
