Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     An open-air platform overlooking the entirety of Azeroth. 
The dragon Nefarian has landed here, his massive form 
blocking out the sun. Primal energy pulses from his 
body, and the air hums with the power of the black 
dragonflight.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
